<h2> Download </h2>
<ul>
<p>
Download the <a href="pdde-cont-@VERSION@.tar.gz">current version (@VERSION@)</a>
</p>
<p>
Download the <a href="pdde-cont-0.9.17.tar.gz">previous version (0.9.17)</a>
</p>
<p>
<b>Note:</b> the two versions are incompatible. From v0.9.18 the function naming scheme in the system definition has been changed. The functions in the system definition code are defined as <tt> extern "C" </tt> to enforce "C" style linking. The namespace specifier <tt> Sys:: </tt> in front of the function name was replaced by the <tt> sys_ </tt> prefix (e.g. <tt> int Sys::ndim(); </tt> &#8594 <tt> extern "C" int sys_ndim();</tt> ).
</p>
<p>
The required ATLAS linear algebra library is available for different platforms in binary form. (The files were collected from different places across the internet.) If the binary for a particular computing platform is not found here, download the source from the <a href="http://math-atlas.sourceforge.net/"> ATLAS web page</a> and follow the compilation instructions.
</p>
